    "tag": "H5",
    "text": "HYDRIDES - A PROVEN TECHNOLOGY FOR HYDROGEN STORAGE",
    "classes": "font_5 wixui-rich-text__text"
  },
  {
    "tag": "H6",
    "text": "SOLIDHYDROGEN specialises in a certain class of hydrides functioning at ambient temperatures, for real life applications. \n\nSOLIDHYDROGEN has developed revolutionary systems and production processes to manufacture hydrides at reduced costs - 10x compared to current market prices - making hydrogen storage, compression and filtration affordable.",
    "classes": "font_6 wixui-rich-text__text"
  },
