  {
    "tag": "H5",
    "text": "CTO",
    "classes": "font_5 wixui-rich-text__text"
  },
  {
    "tag": "P",
    "text": "With three world firsts in over 20 years of hydrogen R&D, Prof Aguey is a world-renowned expert in hydrides development and uses in industry A professor of chemistry at the University of Sydney, Prof Aguey is an advisor to the G7 on the hydrogen development path.",
    "classes": "font_8 wixui-rich-text__text"
  },
  {
    "tag": "H2",
    "text": "Philippe Odouard",
    "classes": "font_2 wixui-rich-text__text"
  },
  {
    "tag": "H5",
    "text": "CEO",
    "classes": "font_5 wixui-rich-text__text"
  },
  {
    "tag": "P",
    "text": "After years at the helm of large defence companies, Mr Odouard was the CEO of two successful listed start-ups in technology involving hardware design, industrialisation and worldwide commercialisation. He managed P/L up to $500m of sales and 700 people.",
    "classes": "font_8 wixui-rich-text__text"
  },
  {
    "tag": "H4",
    "text": "SOLIDHYDROGEN is a startup based in Australia and the US. It has been created with the best worldwide specialists in hydrides and their production.\nPlease email contact@solidhydrogen.tech or click below",
    "classes": "font_4 wixui-rich-text__text"
  },
